Function Documentation

cbWLAN_Band cbWLAN_getBandFromChannel ( cbWLAN_Channel  channel  ) 

Misc.

Returns the correct frequency cbWLAN_Band band based on the input channel.

For cbWLAN_CHANNEL_ALL This function will return cbWLAN_BAND_2_4GHz.

Parameters:
channel The channel to be queried for band.
Returns:
The cbWLAN_Band band for the requested channel.

Returns:

cb_boolean cbWLAN_isNRate ( cbWLAN_Rate  rate  ) 

Checks is the input rate is a 802.11n rate or not.

Parameters:
rate The rate to check
Returns:
TRUE if the input rate is an n-rate. FALSE otherwise.

Checks if a channel is valid.
